Modifications made in this fork:
  - Added MuQ-MuLan reference-audio style transfer:
      * HML MuQ Model Loader (jk_nodes/muq_loader.py)
      * HML Style Embed       (jk_nodes/style_embed.py)
  - Replaced the original "HeartMuLa Music Generator" node with a superset
    "Music Generator" (jk_nodes/style_generator.py) that adds an optional `cmuq`
    style-embedding input. Behavior is identical when `cmuq` is unconnected.
  - Rebranded all reused node ids with the `JKHeartMuLa*` prefix and the
    `JK-HeartMuLa` category, and namespaced the folder-browser route under
    /jkheartmula/, so this pack can be installed alongside the original.

The bundled `heartlib/` library originates from HeartMuLa/heartlib
(https://github.com/HeartMuLa/heartlib). MuQ-MuLan is from OpenMuQ
(https://github.com/tencent-ailab/MuQ).
